Renitec is also used for the prevention of symptomatic heart failure. In many heart failure patients who have symptoms, Renitec slows the worsening of heart failure and reduces the need for hospitalization for heart failure. Renitec also helps some of these patients to live longer. In many patients with early-stage heart failure, before symptoms develop, Renitec helps to prevent weakened cardiac performance and delay the onset of symptoms (for example, shortness of breath, tiredness after light physical activities such as walking, or swelling of the ankles and feet). These patients may need fewer hospitalizations for heart failure. When taking Renitec, some patients with heart failure may be at lower risk of suffering a heart attack (myocardial infarction).
